    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/6b501db9ac3a12952e6d47c3636bbc18.poster.avif?t=1765230513\" width=616 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/6b501db9ac3a12952e6d47c3636bbc18.webm?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/6b501db9ac3a12952e6d47c3636bbc18.mp4?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Ever wondered what it’s like to be a sausage in a museum? Now’s your chance! Take control of our oblong hero on their journey through a surreal art exhibit. Face bizarre challenges, gravity-defying sculptures, and mind-bending installations in an adventure for the most intellectual of art connoisseurs.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE THE MUSEUM<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3dd6869d05a88a24c0bcf082aa39e32.poster.avif?t=1765230513\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3dd6869d05a88a24c0bcf082aa39e32.webm?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3dd6869d05a88a24c0bcf082aa39e32.mp4?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter physics-based challenges that require patience and precision. Each move is a careful balance between progress and slipping back to the beginning of the exhibition. But every victory comes with its own delicious reward : becoming a true art connoisseur.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE THE SAUSAGE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3352343dd5c1cd67c424e4baef417a5.poster.avif?t=1765230513\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3352343dd5c1cd67c424e4baef417a5.webm?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230820/extras/a3352343dd5c1cd67c424e4baef417a5.mp4?t=1765230513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With controls crafted to feel immersive, you will feel like a real sausage. Every roll and flip feels organic - although the sausage is anything but. Oh yeah, and you can <i>yeet</i> yourself if you're willing to take risks.<br><br>If you ever wanted a game that makes fun of the pretentiousness of the contemporary art world, while you embody your favorite steamed meal, you've arrived.<br><br><strong>Art can be challenging.</strong></p>",
